berlegungen zur Richterbindung und Richterfreiheit sowie mit aktuellen Entwicklungen in der Rechtsprechung und Gesetzgebung zum Familienrecht.  aThe balance between law and judicial power has not only inspired legal debates, but also has broad sociopolitical implications. This volume starts with a look at 19th century legal history, followed by a presentation of the judicial models of the 20th century and the highly topical issues of constitutional law, legal theory, and family law.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Feb 2023) 4aGesetzgebung. 4aRechtefreiheit. 4aRechtssprechung. 4aRichterbindung. 7aHISTORY / Social History.2bisacsh1 aAuer, Marietta, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHaferkamp, Hans-Peter, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRottleuthner, Hubert, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRöthel, Anne, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSchorkopf, Frank, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSchumann, Eva, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aSellert, Wolfgang, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2020 Part 1z978311069627108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020z9783110704518oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2020z9783110704525oZDB-23-DEG0 cEPUBz97831106501500 cprintz978311064999440uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311065404240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110654042423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110654042/original  a978-3-11-069627-1  DG Plus DeG Package 2020 Part 1b2020  aEBA_B